{"tid":1477482,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教協明集會及遊行 獲警方發出「不反對通知書」","createTime":"2019-08-16T06:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T13:14:32.000Z","uid":212626,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0e0f774208737736ec23be73cf58afcdb0c42a44","tid":1477482,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:42:51.000Z","msg":"教協發起星期六教育界集會及遊行, 要求政府立即回應民間5大訴求,包括成立獨立調查委員會, 徹查由修訂逃犯條例所引伸的風波, 已獲警方發出「不反對通知書」.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">行動主題是「守護下一代, 為良知發聲」, 大會將會在星期六11時, 在中環遮打花園舉行集會, 11時半遊行到禮賓府, 教協呼籲參與者穿黑色上衣出席, 以最和平和理性的方式表達訴求.</span><br />\n<br />\n對於有學生組織發起開學日罷課, 教協副會長葉建源表示教協認為, 大專學生有足夠成熟程度, 自行決定是否及如何罷課, 而中學生對社會事件的獨立判斷能力參差, 所以不會推動罷課, 或要求學生作政治表態. 如果有中學生提出罷課的要求, 教協建議學校按過去的先例, 安排學生在校內停課, 如學生希望在校外停課, 可按一般請假方式處理, 例如提交家長信證明.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20190816135325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20190816135325&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjalytC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=f2eb3cea\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20190816135325</a>"},{"pid":"d1a4139f09b2ba177dc4f91bc2e76378ef15b632","tid":1477482,"uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:43:27.000Z","msg":"【8.17 教育界遊行 守護下一代 為良知發聲】<br />\n<br />\n「為了香港的下一代，你，願意站出來嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n在過去兩個月，香港人多次走上街頭，要求政府就五大訴求作出回應。然而，政府一直漠視港人意見，警方更多次向遊行示威發出反對通知書，剝奪市民集會和表達意見的權利。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，警方處理大型示威的手法屢受批評，多次以過量武力引致大量市民及記者受傷，甚至以暴動、非法集結等罪名拘捕及檢控示威者，導致警民衝突日益加劇。過去兩個月有超過400人被警方拘捕，當中有教師，也有不少年輕人，據傳媒報導，被捕人士甚至包括一名13歲的學生。另外，警方以「藏有攻擊性武器」為由拘捕浸大學生，更引起社會的廣泛質疑。<br />\n<br />\n面對政府的不回應和不作為，教協發起8月17日舉行教育界遊行，我們呼籲教師積極參與，守護我城的下一代，為良知發聲。<br />\n<br />\n遊行詳情：<br />\n日期：8月17日<br />\n時間：上午11時集會、11時半起步<br />\n路線：中環遮打花園至禮賓府<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C0MEbCk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC0MEbCk.jpg&h=d940df0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67bdd029bd6babc69746b3850c57fb1c10e8c8d9","tid":1477482,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:47:51.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aa99e81ebd6bfc0b28edf54de26963bec748ffd8","tid":1477482,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:49:09.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"1224be48662f4060eac60de8d8827336d8b361b4","tid":1477482,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:49:19.000Z","msg":"教育界<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e78fed957dfb7c7be7bac45887f9cf40c4112f","tid":1477482,"uid":112748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:52:28.000Z","msg":"816㩒錢 816遮打見 818維園見"},{"pid":"c7bce847f3c5c210bf4e363e8f09a3a02b42936f","tid":1477482,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:53:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">超人更進化版本：<br />\n<br />\n大台之瓜，何堪再立！！<br />\n<br />\n大台早已成歷史，無謂再為維撚為收割為獨賣，再扮膠扮假理性吧！！！</span></strong></span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab0e4e3fe8c86d064e471e0c96fa01c5e98fecc","tid":1477482,"uid":99277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:54:29.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"139104b9136ff8bfff32ffdafab3bd209896384a","tid":1477482,"uid":279616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:55:51.000Z","msg":"推到漫山遍野連儂牆818五大訴求文宣（追究721 85 811），重申七一宣言，定立死線<br />\n<br />\n唔係仇警，大家一定要清楚知道點解要清算警隊。警暴（濫捕、濫告、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱<br />\n<br />\n所以，絕對唔需要否認自己係針對警隊，針對警隊就係對準政權。唔通你淨係針對林鄭、唔針對政制，就會有雙普選？<br />\n<br />\n#唔撤就罷<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買罷課<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港四罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#解散警隊<br />\n#永遠抵制元朗荃灣北角所有商戶<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"8cdb409edd9bc028259224426a1a0948127904d9","tid":1477482,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qoXG9tj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqoXG9tj.jpg&h=b6db4e46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a7865257159685427d0f00a14aa381d312e2208","tid":1477482,"uid":276162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:56:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0WQd7h.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0WQd7h.gif&h=2f8b1f58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1aff43cb40a2a2467f240f3def3968cdf8577187","tid":1477482,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:58:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UZFUK16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUZFUK16.jpg&h=0fc65135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkptunion/photos/a.622869427788003/2918760924865497/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkptunion%2Fphotos%2Fa.622869427788003%2F2918760924865497%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjalytC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=7de179df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkptunion/photos/a.622869427788003/2918760924865497/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\nUpdate番張新嘅先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21001fa4c04c7d908a4c5bf2c547b4d1990b3a9","tid":1477482,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":